  <main class="hero">
    <h1>Journal daily.<br/>Get scored nightly.<br/>Face the truth weekly.</h1>
    <p class="tagline">An AI accountability partner built on Stoic philosophy. Not a feelings diary. A discipline system.</p>

    <div id="waitlist" class="waitlist-section">
      <form action="https://n8n-u6v4.onrender.com/webhook/aurelius-waitlist" method="POST" class="waitlist-form">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required class="email-input" />
        <button type="submit" class="cta-button">Join the Waitlist</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Morning Intention</h3>
        <p>Start each day with a Stoic prompt. Set your standard before the day sets it for you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Nightly Scoring</h3>
        <p>Rate your Energy, Focus, Physical, and Satisfaction. Honest numbers, not vague feelings.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>AI Judgment</h3>
        <p>At 10PM, Aurelius reads your day and tells you what you won't tell yourself. Honest before kind.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Weekly Mirror</h3>
        <p>Every Sunday, a narrative that synthesizes your week. Patterns you can't see in the daily noise.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="guides-promo">
      <h2>Learn More</h2>
      <p>Read our <a href="/guides/">guides on AI journaling, Stoic accountability, and building a reflection practice</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <p>Built by <a href="https://sparboesystems.com">Sparboe Systems</a></p>
